body_html: Please bear in mind that the cifar10 tutorial as it is is not meant to be a benchmark. It is meant to show-case a few different features, such as saver and summary. In its current form, it will be CPU-limited, even with GPU. To benchmark, one will have to be more careful and only use essential features.
